* Bug Fix

  * Fix failure to recover from errors during cluster discovery

    Due to the the 5.x - 6.0 migration any errors raised while calling
    the cluster commands for discovering cluster topology were not caught
    as they were raised as exception groups from the client context. This effectively
    meant that the redis cluster implementation was completely broken for any
    non trivial deployment where startup nodes or discovered nodes could be down
    during the initialization phase.
